snippet.title: Puzzle Sigma Walkthrough Cool Math Games
snippet.description: On the playing field there is one mathematical sign to which numbers or other signs can stick. You need to collect mathematical equalities to open the closed door and exit the level. Can collect several expressions at the same time and reverse constructions of numbers and signs.
